{"tid":613992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國軍妹IG嘟嘴照募兵惹議　國防部緊急喊卡","createTime":"2018-04-02T06:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T08:14:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d6d694470b506693f009b44af73588476350b7f","tid":613992,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"國軍近日出現募兵妹等輕佻言辭，甚至還有「馬祖佛系」、軍人路邊擺攤等募兵方式，國防部日前召開檢討會，要求國軍招募文宣應以強調守護家園、保衛國家的　「國軍核心價值」與「軍人專業特性」為主軸，同時要求營連級部隊應專注戰訓本務，招募置重點於留營輔導、新訓轉服、營內懇親宣導及社團活動，嚴禁官兵在街頭宣導、擺攤及實施網路輕佻文宣招募作法，以免影響軍人形象。<br />\n<br />\n國防部指出，2012年「募兵制」實施計畫訂定志願役人力目標為90%，目前國軍兵力總員額為21萬5千，扣除維持員額(學生、入伍、受訓、住院調療及留職停薪)1萬9千及文職、聘僱(7千9百餘人)，軍職編制計18萬8千餘人；以計畫目標90%計算，需16萬9千餘人，推估近3年人力成長，預判2018年底志願役兵力可達15萬2千餘人，編現比為81%，尚缺1萬7千餘人。<br />\n國防部表示，截至3月底各項招募班隊成效均較去年有明顯成長，鑑於近期部份個別街頭招募活動與輕佻文宣等不當行止，國防部已經在3月30日邀集全軍旅級以上單位主官(管)，召開檢討會，要求國軍招募文宣應以強調守護家園、保衛國家之「國軍核心價值」與「軍人專業特性」為主軸，同時要求營連級部隊應專注戰訓本務，招募置重點於留營輔導、新訓轉服、營內懇親宣導及社團活動，嚴禁官兵在街頭宣導、擺攤及實施網路輕佻文宣招募作法，以免影響軍人形象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20180402/1327105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20180402%2F1327105&d=qVPnPxya8ceNoUVqXCKWBNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7b43170c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20180402%2F1327105&h=3fc9b8ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20180402/1327105</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180402/640_efd7ef20c8e3d36fdaa470563e543241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180402%2F640_efd7ef20c8e3d36fdaa470563e543241.jpg&h=3c1761aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180402/640_08f488a6835f83fb7eb94e65ebe96682.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180402%2F640_08f488a6835f83fb7eb94e65ebe96682.jpg&h=f0a948d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891df7d306379f2394a13b0baeaca3f2702e5b50","tid":613992,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"好想收服佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baacd00adf3cdbc071186e1d0345b7716009fcf","tid":613992,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12e01defffd33de87890714a28b6065a2a940f6","tid":613992,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"係咪暗示緊有特殊服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04be02a5ed5bd8c49cfa92a056e9314e36bba6e4","tid":613992,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"第二幅好似大陸d保安咁既喂"},{"pid":"0df214242a26e3c978b6666de953c8a6669c79e0","tid":613992,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"條裙咁短，方便長官操炮"},{"pid":"04491b78f3fc7ed45643ce04127ccf5921e28d8f","tid":613992,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"891df7d306379f2394a13b0baeaca3f2702e5b50","tid":613992,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"好想收服佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e483f0bae7aa2e55ed96c1927bab42d9c1526f0",